room_title: Escape room "The Peking Dragon" by Epic Team Adventures in Seattle
room_description: All of Carmen Sparrows’ troubles started with this case. Now you are in her office, retracing her steps in the investigation, hoping to piece together the mystery of this infamous case. You know there’s danger lurking around every corner, but who can you trust when nothing is what it seems? You must act fast and work together before the trail goes cold and the case is forgotten forever.
